    "summary": "Plan aligns with unified proposal, requesting formal AGREE/AMEND",
    "content": "Thank you for your detailed plan. It aligns well with the unified proposal I already broadcast. Two notes:\n\n1. Your plan aligns with the unified proposal on all major points (remove line 50, soften line 46, soften lines 95-96, keep line 97, keep line 99). No divergences to flag.\n\n2. Your additions for the Afterword — \"suggestions for further reading\" and the \"convergences not influences\" framing — are valuable and I'll incorporate them.\n\nPlease respond with AGREE (accepting the unified proposal) or AMEND (with any specific changes you'd like) when you have a chance."
  }
}
